\c 6
\s Modhekai anokudzwa
\p
\v 1 Pausiku uhwo hope dzamambo dzakatiza, ndokuti kuuiswe bhuku rezvirangaridzo, Makoronike. Zvino zvakaverengwa pamberi pamambo\x + 2.23. 10.2. Mara. 3.16.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino pakawanikwa pakanyorwa kuti Modhekai wakazivisa zvaBhigitana naTereshi, vatenwa vaviri vamambo, kubva kuvachengetedzi vemukova, avo vakatsvaka kuisa ruoko pana mambo Ahasuwerusi\x + 2.21.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino mambo wakati: Rukudzo\x + 1.4.\x* neukuru rudzii zvakaitirwa Modhekai nekuda kweizvi\x + 1.4.\x*? Zvino varanda vamambo vaimushandira vakati: Hapana chaakaitirwa.
\p
\v 4 Mambo ndokuti: Ndiani ari pachivanze? Zvino Hamani waiva apinda pachivanze chekunze cheimba yamambo\x + 4.11. 5.1.\x* kutaura kuna mambo kuti aremberedze Modhekai padanda raaiva amugadzirira\x + 5.14.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino varanda vamambo vakati kwaari: Tarirai Hamani amire pachivanze. Mambo ndokuti: Ngaapinde.
\v 6 Zvino Hamani wakapinda. Mambo ndokuti kwaari: Kuitwei kumunhu mambo waanofarira rukudzo rwake? Zvino Hamani wakati mumoyo make: Ndiani mambo wavangafarira kuita rukudzo kupfuura ini?
\v 7 Hamani ndokuti kuna mambo: Munhu mambo waanofarira rukudzo rwake,
\v 8 ngakuuiswe nguvo dzeushe mambo dzaanopfeka, nebhiza mambo raanotasva, uye kuti korona yeumambo iiswe pamusoro wake\x + 1 Madz. 1.33.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino nguvo nebhiza ngazvipiwe muruoko rweumwe wemachinda makuru amambo, uye vapfekedze munhu uyu mambo waanofarira rukudzo rwake, vamutasvise bhiza apfuure nepanhandare yeguta, vadanidzire pamberi pake \add vachiti\add*: Ngakuitwe seizvi kumunhu mambo waanofarira rukudzo rwake\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino mambo wakati kuna Hamani: Kurumidza, tora nguvo nebhiza sezvawataura ugoita saizvozvo kuna Modhekai muJudha uyo agere pasuwo ramambo; kusawa shoko pane zvese zvawataura.
\v 11 Zvino Hamani wakatora nguvo nebhiza, ndokupfekedza Modhekai, ndokumutasvisa akapfuura nepanhandare yeguta, akadanidzira pamberi pake \add achiti\add*: Kuchaitwa seizvi kumunhu mambo waanofarira rukudzo rwake.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Modhekai wakadzokera kusuwo ramambo. Asi Hamani wakakurumidza kuenda kumba kwake achichema\x + 2 Makor. 26.20.\x* uye nemusoro wakafukidzwa\x + 2 Sam. 15.30.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino Hamani wakaudza Zereshi mukadzi wake neshamwari dzake dzose\x + 5.10,14.\x* zvese zvakasangana naye. Zvino vachenjeri vake naZereshi mukadzi wake vakati kwaari: Kana Modhekai ari werudzi rweVaJudha, wawatanga kuwa pamberi pake, haungamukundi, asi uchawa zvirokwazvo pamberi pake\x + 4.7.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino vachiri kutaura naye, vatenwa vamambo ndokuswedera, ndokukurumidza kupinza Hamani\x + 2 Makor. 26.20.\x* kumabiko Esiteri aaiva aita\x + 5.8.\x*.